data.description: Bonsall by the Beach! Private Elevator! 4 Car Garage !Hidden Gem-True Must See to Believe!*VIEWS FROM THE TOP!*POSSIBLE 3rd BEDROOM!*PRIVATE GATED COMMUNITY!*UNPARALLELED PANORAMIC VIEWS!*NO NEIGHBORS IN FRONT, BEHIND, OR TO THE LEFT!*PRIVATE END-UNIT!*Welcome Home ! This stunning 2 Bed / 2 Bath, 2,448 Sq. Ft. property sits in the exclusive gated community of The Terraces ! As you enter, you're greeted by a bright, formal entry way with new, custom flooring, skylight and PRIVATE ELEVATOR ACCESS ! The oversized living area is ideal for entertaining and opens to spacious sunroom with wall-to-wall windows which offer panoramic hillside and mountain views ! Wake up and enjoy your morning coffee watching the horses on the San Luis Rey Racetrack ! Or relax with your favorite glass of wine watching the gorgeous sunset ! The kitchen is upgraded throughout, and features custom cabinetry, pots & pan drawers, beautiful granite counters, new stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, and opens to the wet bar and dining room ! The backyard is beautifully landscaped and hardscaped with custom pavers, low-maintenance plants, and soothing water feature ! The primary bedroom is oversized with private access to the backyard and features an extra large walk-in closet with custom built-ins. The en-suite primary bath boast His & Her custom, mirrored vanities, extra storage areas, dual sinks, granite counters, bath and shower ! The secondary suite is very large and open and complimented with large walk-in closet with built-ins, and large, private balcony with breathtaking hillside views ! Feel the ocean breeze from your bedroom ! Extra large 4 car garage ! Plus elevator that brings you to the main level ! Individual laundry room ! The HOA amenities include 2 pools, spa, grounds maintenance, water, trash, exterior paint, lawn and gardening, roof, plumbing, insurance coverage, and security ! This stunning, exclusive community is minutes away from World Class beaches, high-end shopping, amazing local restaurants, and all within an award-winning school district ! This gorgeous home has everything you want !
